WEBVTT

00:04:08.799 --> 00:04:14.159
Good

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:17.279
morning, family. Thank you for joining

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:18.880
us again today. We'll go over some

00:04:17.279 --> 00:04:22.000
of the things the Lord showed us

00:04:18.880 --> 00:04:23.680
yesterday in prayer and then we'll

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:25.199
just jump in the river. I know a lot of

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:26.400
you have a lot of things you're going to

00:04:25.199 --> 00:04:28.880
be doing today because we're getting

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:31.758
ready to celebrate the Fourth of July in

00:04:28.880 --> 00:04:35.040
America. And so we say, 'Happy birthday, America.'I

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:37.840
believe

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:40.160
it's an exciting time. I

00:04:37.840 --> 00:04:42.159
love this time of year; I love it.

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:43.520
My birthday's today, so I get

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:45.759
excited about that.

00:04:43.520 --> 00:04:48.880
Thank you, I

00:04:45.759 --> 00:04:50.479
appreciate that. I woke up early this

00:04:48.880 --> 00:04:52.240
morning and was talking to the

00:04:50.479 --> 00:04:53.919
Lord about my life and things that the

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:56.639
Lord has done this year, just being

00:04:53.919 --> 00:04:58.080
grateful for everything that I have and

00:04:56.639 --> 00:05:01.360
that the Lord has blessed me with good

00:04:58.080 --> 00:05:03.039
health. I'm so thankful

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:09.039
not just for living, but for living well—that

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:10.960
your health is good.

00:05:09.039 --> 00:05:12.479
I know everybody has

00:05:10.960 --> 00:05:14.799
something they're overcoming and you're

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:16.560
believing God for stuff, but for the

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:18.800
most part, Lord, You've kept

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:23.639
me sound and whole. Thank

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:23.639
you. He

00:05:34.800 --> 00:05:40.400
talked about being satisfied

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:41.680
and started

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:43.919
talking to me about elders and some of

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:45.600
the ones who were going home.

00:05:43.919 --> 00:05:48.880
He started telling me, 'This one

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:50.479
will live to 78.'I

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:52.080
said, 'Well, that's not too much

00:05:50.479 --> 00:05:55.320
longer.

00:05:56.479 --> 00:06:01.440
Why are they going to go home

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:04.759
at that time?'He said, 'Because

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:04.759
they're satisfied.'I

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:09.360
said, 'Satisfied? What does that

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:12.400
have to do with anything?'He

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:15.520
said, 'With long life, I will satisfy

00:06:12.400 --> 00:06:20.318
you. And when you're satisfied, Brandon,

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:23.280
you can come home.'Are you satisfied?

00:06:20.319 --> 00:06:25.520
He said you can

00:06:23.280 --> 00:06:27.359
petition Me for more years, but

00:06:25.520 --> 00:06:28.880
when you are satisfied and

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:31.120
walking with Me in ministry, doing

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:33.600
what you're supposed to be doing, He

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:35.600
said, 'The number of your

00:06:33.600 --> 00:06:37.120
days I will fulfill. I

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:39.120
will let you live until you're

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:41.199
satisfied. When you are satisfied, I'll

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:44.160
bring you home. I'll give you

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:46.560
120.'He

00:06:44.160 --> 00:06:48.479
was talking to me

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:50.400
about being satisfied with life.

00:06:59.280 --> 00:07:06.799
I said I'm not satisfied at that

00:07:02.639 --> 00:07:08.639
age; I want to occupy. I'm not in a hurry

00:07:06.800 --> 00:07:12.000
to go to the other side if You're not coming in the

00:07:08.639 --> 00:07:14.479
Rapture,

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:16.160
because I know there's so

00:07:14.479 --> 00:07:17.680
many people that are dying and going to

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:20.000
hell.

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:22.160
I'm not criticizing; that's

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:24.479
just where I'm at. Maybe I'll be

00:07:22.160 --> 00:07:28.160
different when I get that old.

00:07:24.479 --> 00:07:31.758
Right now, because

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:33.759
I'm only 46 today, I'm not even near. I

00:07:31.759 --> 00:07:36.720
feel like I just started my

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:40.240
race. So I say, 'My goodness, give me double,'because

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:43.120
I see so many people

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:46.240
going to hell. Yesterday we

00:07:43.120 --> 00:07:49.960
had 34 people give their heart to Jesus

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:49.960
Christ on our channel.

00:07:54.080 --> 00:08:00.878
There's a tenderness to it

00:07:58.240 --> 00:08:03.599
because it's just the beginning of what

00:08:00.879 --> 00:08:05.120
the Lord is doing. I know

00:08:03.599 --> 00:08:07.199
there'll be a lot more people

00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:08.720
born again over the next couple days

00:08:07.199 --> 00:08:10.319
watching that video, especially on my

00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:11.759
other channels. I have seven other

00:08:10.319 --> 00:08:13.520
channels in South Korea.

00:08:11.759 --> 00:08:15.039
It's so wonderful to see

00:08:13.520 --> 00:08:17.440
people that are Buddhists give

00:08:15.039 --> 00:08:19.039
their heart to Jesus Christ.

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:22.000
Then when you have the Portuguese

00:08:19.039 --> 00:08:24.479
channel and the Brazilian, the Lord

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:26.560
said to pray over

00:08:24.479 --> 00:08:29.360
the young man that's running it. I

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:32.000
saw a new David rising up in Brazil and

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:34.479
He said, 'Pray for the people of Brazil;

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:37.519
there are so many of them.'As I

00:08:34.479 --> 00:08:39.919
talked to Pastor Maldonado,

00:08:37.519 --> 00:08:42.640
he was talking about

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:45.680
souls and

00:08:42.640 --> 00:08:51.120
his goal of setting

00:08:45.680 --> 00:08:54.399
it up for a million

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:56.480
people to go to Cuba and have a

00:08:54.399 --> 00:08:58.640
revival. He's already getting it

00:08:56.480 --> 00:09:01.120
ready; they're already preparing

00:08:58.640 --> 00:09:03.600
financially for

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:06.560
what God is about to do in the Latino

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:08.880
community. It inspires me.

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:11.439
It

00:09:08.880 --> 00:09:13.120
stretches me because he gave me the counts

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:15.200
of all the people that

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:21.040
have been born again in

00:09:17.680 --> 00:09:23.920
his ministry—14 million people in over 30 years.

00:09:21.040 --> 00:09:26.240
I thought, 'Wow.'He gave me the

00:09:23.920 --> 00:09:30.560
list, giving all the glory to

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:33.279
the Lord. Just thinking about

00:09:30.560 --> 00:09:35.199
making a lasting impact, changing

00:09:33.279 --> 00:09:37.279
a generation for

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:39.839
Jesus, and

00:09:37.279 --> 00:09:43.200
wanting to leave your mark on this world.

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:47.120
I believe He's coming,

00:09:45.839 --> 00:09:48.640
ladies and gentlemen. Don't get me

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:51.839
wrong, but I know there have been generations—Sister Woodworth-Etter

00:09:48.640 --> 00:09:53.519
believed He

00:09:51.839 --> 00:09:55.040
was coming back in her timeframe in the

00:09:53.519 --> 00:09:57.440
1800s

00:09:55.040 --> 00:10:01.199
and had signs 'Jesus is coming soon'on

00:09:57.440 --> 00:10:03.200
her banners. Kathryn Kuhlman

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:05.600
felt that she was

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:08.399
coming in her time.

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:11.360
I believe Brother Hagin felt that he was

00:10:08.399 --> 00:10:13.360
coming in his time—Kenneth Hagin. So

00:10:11.360 --> 00:10:15.600
you have a generation of people that

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:18.000
have always had that urgency inside of themselves

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:21.040
because there's no

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:23.920
time with the Lord. He has

00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:26.000
long patience for the harvest

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:28.319
because He doesn't want

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:30.800
any man to perish but all to come

00:10:28.320 --> 00:10:32.560
to repentance. So what is He looking

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:35.680
for?

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:37.839
What is on the Father's heart?

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:41.439
That was my big thing today:

00:10:37.839 --> 00:10:43.440
'What's the number?'I

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:46.079
know there will be people

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:49.040
here in the Tribulation, but what's the

00:10:46.079 --> 00:10:51.599
number You're looking for?

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:54.399
What's the tipping point? What are we

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:56.320
waiting on? You say You're waiting on us

00:10:54.399 --> 00:10:58.160
to bring in the harvest. What's the

00:10:56.320 --> 00:11:00.240
number? Because I'm a numbers person.

00:10:58.160 --> 00:11:02.480
I'm always thinking,

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:04.000
'Show me what You're looking at

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:05.680
so we can at least...'You know when you

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:08.000
have those

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:11.120
fundraisers and you see the thermometer

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:12.480
and they

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:13.680
fill in the red as it goes

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:17.040
up? I'm

00:11:13.680 --> 00:11:20.079
thinking, at least give me a goal:

00:11:17.040 --> 00:11:22.560
14 million, 15 million, 16—no,

00:11:20.079 --> 00:11:24.880
that's not enough. A billion, two

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:26.880
billion, three billion.

00:11:24.880 --> 00:11:28.720
What's on Your heart? He doesn't

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:30.880
want any man to perish. Well, we've

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:32.959
got a problem—I'm

00:11:30.880 --> 00:11:34.399
just teasing—because I'm thinking there are

00:11:32.959 --> 00:11:35.518
8 billion people and I know there's

00:11:34.399 --> 00:11:39.839
going to be a lot of them in the

00:11:35.519 --> 00:11:41.440
Tribulation. But

00:11:39.839 --> 00:11:45.279
I'm stretching out and believing God for

00:11:41.440 --> 00:11:46.800
big. I want

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:49.120
to reach the nations for Jesus.

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:51.359
That's why I'm inspired by people

00:11:49.120 --> 00:11:53.120
who are already doing it and touching

00:11:51.360 --> 00:11:56.160
people's lives.

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:57.839
It's exciting whenever I get your

00:11:56.160 --> 00:12:00.079
emails and you say, 'Braden, you prayed

00:11:57.839 --> 00:12:03.200
for this and I was delivered. I have no

00:12:00.079 --> 00:12:05.439
more pains in my body and

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:08.160
Jesus set me free through your broadcast.

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:09.760
I had demonic oppression and

00:12:08.160 --> 00:12:11.199
depression, and ever since you prayed,

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:12.959
I haven't had it anymore.'Just

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:15.200
hearing the testimonies—Diana

00:12:12.959 --> 00:12:16.880
said, 'You hear a

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:18.480
lot of the negative, Braden, but I want

00:12:16.880 --> 00:12:20.240
to go through all the positive ones

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:21.920
today.

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:24.560
I want to show you the ones that are

00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:27.040
being impacted by the ministry versus

00:12:24.560 --> 00:12:29.680
the knuckleheads that want to be mean. I

00:12:27.040 --> 00:12:31.519
want to show you the ones whose

00:12:29.680 --> 00:12:33.279
lives are being forever changed, and it's

00:12:31.519 --> 00:12:35.040
changing their whole family because of

00:12:33.279 --> 00:12:37.120
the ministry, Brandon.'So

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:39.519
she read through some of those and it

00:12:37.120 --> 00:12:40.880
blessed me because I don't

00:12:39.519 --> 00:12:44.000
have time to read all that. She reads a

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:46.160
lot of it and I just say,

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:48.399
'God bless it.'I'm

00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:50.160
excited to be here and thankful to

00:12:48.399 --> 00:12:53.600
hear the testimonies of what the Lord

00:12:50.160 --> 00:12:56.160
has done on this little YouTube

00:12:53.600 --> 00:12:58.639
channel.

00:12:56.160 --> 00:13:01.600
We started out three years ago

00:12:58.639 --> 00:13:03.360
and here we are now. The

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:05.760
Lord said, 'I want you to go on mornings

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:08.959
now, and then I'll grow it to 20,000

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:11.519
every single day.'20,000 on a live

00:13:08.959 --> 00:13:12.800
stream. I want to grow it to 20,000. So

00:13:11.519 --> 00:13:14.480
that's my number. I'm believing for

00:13:12.800 --> 00:13:15.839
20,000 people to come on in on a live

00:13:14.480 --> 00:13:18.720
stream and pray with me every single

00:13:15.839 --> 00:13:21.279
time at once. The Lord said, "I'll

00:13:18.720 --> 00:13:24.079
give you the largest prayer army in the

00:13:21.279 --> 00:13:26.880
world. A million people will pray with

00:13:24.079 --> 00:13:29.519
you on a consecutive basis. Believe me

00:13:26.880 --> 00:13:32.399
for it."So I'm believing for a million-man and -woman

00:13:29.519 --> 00:13:34.880
prayer army to pray over

00:13:32.399 --> 00:13:37.440
the nations, that when we pray over

00:13:34.880 --> 00:13:40.000
presidents and

00:13:37.440 --> 00:13:41.440
politicians around the world, we can

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:44.240
change things through the power of

00:13:41.440 --> 00:13:46.320
prayer. I truly believe that the

00:13:44.240 --> 00:13:49.600
authority of the believer is not

00:13:46.320 --> 00:13:51.279
being taught in this generation enough.

00:13:49.600 --> 00:13:52.720
We have people like Sister Billie who

00:13:51.279 --> 00:13:54.720
will go over it and have her book, and

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:57.680
Brother Hagin, but he went

00:13:54.720 --> 00:13:59.279
home and Billy's getting older, so we

00:13:57.680 --> 00:14:02.079
need another generation, a younger

00:13:59.279 --> 00:14:05.040
generation, grabbing a hold of it. You have

00:14:02.079 --> 00:14:06.959
authority over the devil, and you can

00:14:05.040 --> 00:14:09.920
tread on serpents and scorpions, and

00:14:06.959 --> 00:14:11.760
nothing shall by any means hurt you. I

00:14:09.920 --> 00:14:14.319
believe that we have a covenant-keeping

00:14:11.760 --> 00:14:15.519
God, that whatsoever things we bind on

00:14:14.320 --> 00:14:16.800
earth are bound in heaven, and whatsoever

00:14:15.519 --> 00:14:19.120
things are loosed on earth are loosed in

00:14:16.800 --> 00:14:20.800
heaven. I believe that we have power

00:14:19.120 --> 00:14:22.959
and authority to tread on those serpents

00:14:20.800 --> 00:14:25.359
and scorpions. And the roaring lion that

00:14:22.959 --> 00:14:28.000
he thinks he is, we have authority over

00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:30.560
him. He's a toothless lion; he

00:14:28.000 --> 00:14:33.199
may have a roar, but a lion without

00:14:30.560 --> 00:14:35.518
teeth is not a threat.

00:14:33.199 --> 00:14:38.560
He cannot devour those that are

00:14:35.519 --> 00:14:42.560
underneath the covenant.

00:14:38.560 --> 00:14:45.359
A curse without a cause cannot stand.

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:46.959
Don't give it a cause. Don't open the

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:48.959
doors for the devil to come. If you open

00:14:46.959 --> 00:14:51.839
the door for the devil, he'll come right

00:14:48.959 --> 00:14:53.839
in on top of you. Keep the door shut.

00:14:51.839 --> 00:14:57.040
How do you do that? By fellowship with

00:14:53.839 --> 00:15:01.199
him. Read your Bible and pray. Take

00:14:57.040 --> 00:15:03.199
communion every day. When you get

00:15:01.199 --> 00:15:07.120
real with God, God will become real to

00:15:03.199 --> 00:15:08.800
you. Stop being fake. He knows what

00:15:07.120 --> 00:15:10.880
you're thinking before you even think

00:15:08.800 --> 00:15:12.160
it. He knows what you're going to say

00:15:10.880 --> 00:15:14.160
out of your heart. Out of the abundance

00:15:12.160 --> 00:15:15.439
of the heart, the mouth speaks. He knows

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:18.639
what you're going to say out of your

00:15:15.440 --> 00:15:21.360
mouth before you even say it. You think,

00:15:18.639 --> 00:15:23.680
say, whatever;

00:15:21.360 --> 00:15:26.320
it's about relationship. He knows

00:15:23.680 --> 00:15:28.239
when I'm mad at him. He knows when I'm

00:15:26.320 --> 00:15:32.399
having a bad day. He knows when I'm

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:35.279
upset about what we're going through.

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:36.720
So get real with him. When you get

00:15:35.279 --> 00:15:38.880
real with God—and I'm not trying to tell

00:15:36.720 --> 00:15:41.199
you to be disrespectful; don't ever

00:15:38.880 --> 00:15:42.959
dishonor him—just be real with him

00:15:41.199 --> 00:15:47.359
in your heart: "I'm going through this. I

00:15:42.959 --> 00:15:49.758
need you."The more you say, "I need you,"the

00:15:47.360 --> 00:15:53.120
more you realize that you can't do

00:15:49.759 --> 00:15:56.399
this without him. Humble yourself

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:59.680
underneath his mighty hand. I say, "God,

00:15:56.399 --> 00:16:02.079
help me. I can't do this without you. I

00:15:59.680 --> 00:16:04.160
need you. I need you in every area of my

00:16:02.079 --> 00:16:05.839
life: spiritually, physically,

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:09.000
financially, mentally, emotionally. I

00:16:05.839 --> 00:16:09.000
need you."The

00:16:12.880 --> 00:16:16.320
first thing this

00:16:14.959 --> 00:16:19.319
morning, he said, "Happy birthday,

00:16:16.320 --> 00:16:19.320
Brennan."The

00:16:42.720 --> 00:16:46.759
moment I woke up,

00:16:47.680 --> 00:16:51.800
I could tell he was watching me,

00:16:57.519 --> 00:17:01.560
like he was watching me sleep,

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:22.119
anticipating me waking up.

00:17:41.840 --> 00:17:45.159
I saw

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:51.678
things yesterday in prayer that make you

00:17:49.280 --> 00:17:54.879
realize how close we are

00:17:51.679 --> 00:17:56.960
to the coming of the Lord.

00:17:54.880 --> 00:17:59.600
I'll go into more detail today

00:17:56.960 --> 00:18:01.679
because I try not to hurry it, but I

00:17:59.600 --> 00:18:03.760
give you the details.

00:18:01.679 --> 00:18:07.400
As that angel came in yesterday and

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:07.400
stood right here,

00:18:07.679 --> 00:18:11.039
I was praying and singing that

00:18:09.280 --> 00:18:14.160
song,

00:18:11.039 --> 00:18:15.520
"Holy, Holy, Holy."The

00:18:14.160 --> 00:18:18.080
Lord corrected me. He said, "You're

00:18:15.520 --> 00:18:20.720
letting your mind wander too much."When

00:18:18.080 --> 00:18:23.600
I was praying, he said, "Stop worrying about

00:18:20.720 --> 00:18:26.480
the time clock. Let it die. If they want

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:28.159
to leave, they'll leave,

00:18:26.480 --> 00:18:29.679
but I need you to do something for me today."And

00:18:28.160 --> 00:18:31.840
that's the same thing he said

00:18:29.679 --> 00:18:33.679
today about this because I said,

00:18:31.840 --> 00:18:36.240
"Well, it's my birthday. Do I do a

00:18:33.679 --> 00:18:38.640
video day?"He said, "I need you today

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:40.160
to do this."I said, "Okay, we'll do

00:18:38.640 --> 00:18:43.200
it."So,

00:18:40.160 --> 00:18:45.679
as the angel was

00:18:43.200 --> 00:18:48.559
there yesterday, he said, "I have a

00:18:45.679 --> 00:18:50.480
message for you.

00:18:48.559 --> 00:18:51.840
I want you to say I have a message. The

00:18:50.480 --> 00:18:53.600
Lord wants you to say this."I

00:18:51.840 --> 00:18:55.760
saw him. He was standing right there, and

00:18:53.600 --> 00:18:58.240
he had that golden armor on with that

00:18:55.760 --> 00:19:00.240
helmet on. It had a weird-looking

00:18:58.240 --> 00:19:02.320
hat, a little hair-looking stuff coming

00:19:00.240 --> 00:19:04.640
off the top of his head that looked

00:19:02.320 --> 00:19:06.080
like some kind of feathers. I've

00:19:04.640 --> 00:19:07.919
never seen an angel look like that

00:19:06.080 --> 00:19:12.399
before.

00:19:07.919 --> 00:19:14.000
It's really neat looking,

00:19:12.400 --> 00:19:15.360
but I was seeing it in the spirit. It

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:18.320
wasn't in the natural; I wasn't touching

00:19:15.360 --> 00:19:21.039
it. I'm looking over in the spirit.

00:19:21.039 --> 00:19:26.720
As I was singing, I saw

00:19:24.400 --> 00:19:28.640
the wall, the watchman wall, again.

00:19:26.720 --> 00:19:30.000
This is the second day in a row the Lord

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:32.240
allowed me to see that wall. And he

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:34.000
said, "This is your wall.

00:19:32.240 --> 00:19:36.799
Which door, which portal do you want to

00:19:34.000 --> 00:19:39.280
go down today in prayer?"And he let me

00:19:36.799 --> 00:19:41.760
choose again. But I was sitting there

00:19:39.280 --> 00:19:43.840
singing, and then the angel came

00:19:41.760 --> 00:19:46.720
and he said to me, "The Lord says, sing

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:48.879
the song one more time."I

00:19:46.720 --> 00:19:51.440
started singing it, but

00:19:48.880 --> 00:19:53.360
because I was crying, my voice

00:19:51.440 --> 00:19:55.840
was cracking, and

00:19:53.360 --> 00:19:58.159
I couldn't hit the higher notes.

00:19:58.160 --> 00:20:01.120
After I sang it halfway through, I

00:19:59.760 --> 00:20:03.679
looked to see if he was going to say

00:20:01.120 --> 00:20:06.159
something, and he didn't say anything. Then he

00:20:03.679 --> 00:20:09.160
said, "Sing the song all the way

00:20:06.160 --> 00:20:09.160
through."I

00:20:09.360 --> 00:20:14.080
was just taken aback by it. I was

00:20:11.600 --> 00:20:17.120
like, "Okay."So I sang it again.

00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:20.480
When I got to the end of it, the door

00:20:17.120 --> 00:20:22.239
that he was standing in front of opened,

00:20:20.480 --> 00:20:26.080
and I could see the Father on the

00:20:22.240 --> 00:20:28.720
throne, a big bright light. There was

00:20:26.080 --> 00:20:30.879
a staircase that went down with

00:20:28.720 --> 00:20:33.360
beautiful water that started to flow

00:20:30.880 --> 00:20:35.679
from his throne. This water that looked

00:20:33.360 --> 00:20:37.760
just like living water just started

00:20:35.679 --> 00:20:39.600
flowing down. It was the floodgates

00:20:37.760 --> 00:20:41.840
of the revival.

00:20:39.600 --> 00:20:43.918
It was the flood

00:20:41.840 --> 00:20:45.439
of the major outpouring that's about to

00:20:43.919 --> 00:20:48.240
happen on this earth. It was there;

00:20:45.440 --> 00:20:50.960
I could see it. Then he

00:20:48.240 --> 00:20:52.400
said, "I have a message."The

00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:56.679
angel said, "I have a

00:20:52.400 --> 00:20:56.679
message about Israel."He

00:20:57.360 --> 00:21:08.840
said, "The fig tree is ripe,

00:21:02.720 --> 00:21:08.840
and Ezekiel 38-39 is at the door."The

00:21:09.280 --> 00:21:16.000
fig tree is ripe.

00:21:12.799 --> 00:21:18.639
I saw these vast figs on this fig

00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:21.520
tree that were double the size of a

00:21:18.640 --> 00:21:23.039
normal fig, but they looked beautiful. It

00:21:21.520 --> 00:21:25.039
looked like you could just eat

00:21:23.039 --> 00:21:27.760
the whole tree.

00:21:25.039 --> 00:21:30.960
This tree was massive, and it was upon a

00:21:27.760 --> 00:21:35.520
hill. I could see the

00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:39.679
sun setting on the hill. The sun was

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:41.918
setting on this dispensation of grace.

00:21:39.679 --> 00:21:43.600
Jesus Christ is coming, ladies and

00:21:41.919 --> 00:21:46.720
gentlemen, and it's time to get your

00:21:43.600 --> 00:21:49.439
heart right before him. I saw the fig

00:21:46.720 --> 00:21:52.559
tree. As I was looking into that fig

00:21:49.440 --> 00:21:57.039
tree, the Lord said, "I have scattered

00:21:52.559 --> 00:22:01.280
my people upon the earth, and now is the

00:21:57.039 --> 00:22:03.360
time I will gather them all."He

00:22:01.280 --> 00:22:04.960
was talking about the Jews.

00:22:07.520 --> 00:22:12.480
He said, "I have scattered them

00:22:10.320 --> 00:22:14.320
all over the earth, and now I'm

00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:17.120
going to gather them all."I saw

00:22:14.320 --> 00:22:20.480
persecution coming on the Jewish people.

00:22:17.120 --> 00:22:24.239
I saw a

00:22:20.480 --> 00:22:26.480
mass amount of people coming to

00:22:24.240 --> 00:22:29.760
Israel and Jerusalem and all the area

00:22:26.480 --> 00:22:33.840
in the days ahead. It is a major

00:22:29.760 --> 00:22:38.000
turning of an event. He said as of

00:22:33.840 --> 00:22:40.639
this month—the seventh month—it

00:22:38.000 --> 00:22:43.280
is a significant

00:22:40.640 --> 00:22:46.799
month: the month of July.

00:22:43.280 --> 00:22:50.158
He said this is a significant month of

00:22:46.799 --> 00:22:53.039
an acceleration for

00:22:50.159 --> 00:22:55.679
this next six months:

00:23:04.799 --> 00:23:09.280
July, August, September,

00:23:07.440 --> 00:23:11.120
October, November, and December. Six

00:23:09.280 --> 00:23:14.240
months, yes.

00:23:11.120 --> 00:23:18.239
Over this time frame, I

00:23:14.240 --> 00:23:21.520
saw an acceleration of things: of elders

00:23:18.240 --> 00:23:26.120
going home, of a cleansing of the

00:23:21.520 --> 00:23:26.120
church.

00:23:33.520 --> 00:23:38.960
From July 3rd to

00:23:39.520 --> 00:23:43.760
January 3rd—the first part of

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:46.000
next year—is this time frame of an

00:23:43.760 --> 00:23:49.120
acceleration of things. Thanks, son; I

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:53.520
really appreciate that. As I was

00:23:49.120 --> 00:23:56.000
looking into Israel, I saw a light

00:23:53.520 --> 00:23:58.158
over it with dark in a valley, and I saw

00:23:56.000 --> 00:24:01.280
the bones living. He said, "Can

00:23:58.159 --> 00:24:03.600
these bones live concerning America? Can

00:24:01.280 --> 00:24:06.320
these bones live concerning the

00:24:03.600 --> 00:24:09.600
revival?"I

00:24:06.320 --> 00:24:11.439
was praying over the dry bones

00:24:09.600 --> 00:24:14.320
over the world. Talking about the

00:24:11.440 --> 00:24:16.000
lukewarm, talking about the cold

00:24:14.320 --> 00:24:19.200
Christians,

00:24:16.000 --> 00:24:22.159
the people who know better: it's time to

00:24:19.200 --> 00:24:24.159
come home. It's time to become on fire

00:24:22.159 --> 00:24:26.240
for Jesus.

00:24:24.159 --> 00:24:28.720
He's coming back for a bride without

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:33.120
spot or wrinkle that is holy

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:34.400
and brought to his side, not a harlot.

00:24:33.120 --> 00:24:38.399
You're not in bed with two different

00:24:34.400 --> 00:24:41.520
things. It's all him and none of us,

00:24:38.400 --> 00:24:43.440
right? We need to be sold out to him,

00:24:41.520 --> 00:24:46.559
and we don't have a compromise of the

00:24:43.440 --> 00:24:48.799
world inside of us. It's time to come up

00:24:46.559 --> 00:24:51.039
higher in our prayer life. It's time to

00:24:48.799 --> 00:24:52.879
come up higher in our relationship

00:24:51.039 --> 00:24:55.440
with the Lord.

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:57.440
We need to be all-in.

00:24:55.440 --> 00:25:00.080
As I saw the fig tree

00:24:57.440 --> 00:25:01.760
upon the hill, I saw the water coming

00:25:00.080 --> 00:25:03.360
down, and I saw the revival, and I saw

00:25:01.760 --> 00:25:05.360
creative miracles. And

00:25:03.360 --> 00:25:07.600
they said,

00:25:05.360 --> 00:25:10.479
'Do not become familiar with the

00:25:07.600 --> 00:25:12.240
miracles that you're about to see.

00:25:10.480 --> 00:25:14.640
Don't take them as just another miracle.'Honor them; every miracle is to be holy. Don't say, 'It's just

00:25:12.240 --> 00:25:18.000
another set

00:25:14.640 --> 00:25:20.000
of

00:25:18.000 --> 00:25:22.480
blind

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:25.120
eyes;

00:25:22.480 --> 00:25:29.000
it's just another dead man being raised.

00:25:25.120 --> 00:25:29.000
I've seen that before.'Every

00:25:29.279 --> 00:25:35.440
miracle is a gift from God. It's a

00:25:33.120 --> 00:25:38.399
blessing. It's his grace. He said, 'For

00:25:35.440 --> 00:25:41.760
now, show me your glory and I will pass

00:25:38.400 --> 00:25:43.679
by with my goodness and my mercy on this

00:25:41.760 --> 00:25:47.840
generation.'Oral

00:25:43.679 --> 00:25:49.679
Roberts had his; Jack Coe had his;

00:25:47.840 --> 00:25:53.199
William Branham,

00:25:49.679 --> 00:25:54.799
Kenneth Hagin, Kathryn Kuhlman. But the Lord

00:25:53.200 --> 00:25:58.720
said, 'I'm raising up a new generation, a

00:25:54.799 --> 00:26:01.200
new era of people

00:25:58.720 --> 00:26:03.200
right now that you're about to see, who

00:26:01.200 --> 00:26:05.760
are the closers,

00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:08.799
built for pressure.'He said, 'This is

00:26:05.760 --> 00:26:11.360
my dream team.'It's

00:26:08.799 --> 00:26:13.039
like it was in the '90s when

00:26:11.360 --> 00:26:14.799
we had Michael Jordan, Magic

00:26:13.039 --> 00:26:16.158
Johnson, and Larry Bird

00:26:14.799 --> 00:26:18.480
playing basketball for the

00:26:16.159 --> 00:26:20.880
Olympics. He's putting in his dream

00:26:18.480 --> 00:26:22.159
team.

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:23.760
And ladies and gentlemen, there's many

00:26:22.159 --> 00:26:25.919
of you that would be the dream team.

00:26:23.760 --> 00:26:29.679
He's raising up prophetic voices with

00:26:25.919 --> 00:26:31.919
accuracy and without being flaky.

00:26:29.679 --> 00:26:34.880
There's too much flakiness, charismatic

00:26:31.919 --> 00:26:37.279
weirdness, and the Lord's going to strip

00:26:34.880 --> 00:26:39.600
away this charismatic weirdness. It's

00:26:37.279 --> 00:26:41.200
embarrassing.

00:26:39.600 --> 00:26:43.520
You have a group of people

00:26:41.200 --> 00:26:45.360
that don't know how to hear the Holy Ghost.

00:26:43.520 --> 00:26:47.039
It's weird; there's a lot of

00:26:45.360 --> 00:26:49.678
weirdness. And the Lord said, 'I'm

00:26:47.039 --> 00:26:52.400
flipping the status quo

00:26:49.679 --> 00:26:54.880
concerning finances.'The devil's crowd

00:26:52.400 --> 00:26:57.120
had it too long. And if you listen to

00:26:54.880 --> 00:26:59.440
what he's telling

00:26:57.120 --> 00:27:01.279
you to do, he said, 'I'll give you more

00:26:59.440 --> 00:27:03.919
than enough to do what I need you to do,

00:27:01.279 --> 00:27:06.000
exceedingly abundantly above all

00:27:03.919 --> 00:27:09.039
that you'd ask or think.'It's time to

00:27:06.000 --> 00:27:10.880
believe him for bigger. Well, 'I'm just

00:27:09.039 --> 00:27:14.760
believing for my bills to be paid.'You're

00:27:10.880 --> 00:27:14.760
believing too small.

00:27:15.440 --> 00:27:20.240
It's not just about 'us four and no more.'It's

00:27:18.559 --> 00:27:22.158
about stretching out and believing

00:27:20.240 --> 00:27:24.320
God for exceedingly abundantly above all

00:27:22.159 --> 00:27:26.720
that you'd ask or think. Why? Because God is a covenant-keeping

00:27:24.320 --> 00:27:31.120
God. And if God did it

00:27:26.720 --> 00:27:35.600
for Abraham, he'll do it for you.

00:27:31.120 --> 00:27:37.840
If God did it for

00:27:37.840 --> 00:27:43.439
Solomon,

00:27:41.520 --> 00:27:45.440
how much more will he do it for you? If

00:27:43.440 --> 00:27:47.600
Solomon was underneath the old covenant

00:27:45.440 --> 00:27:49.520
and you're underneath the new, how much

00:27:47.600 --> 00:27:52.320
more will God do it for you if you

00:27:49.520 --> 00:27:54.960
believe him for it? But it's produced from seedtime

00:27:52.320 --> 00:27:56.559
and harvest. And a lot

00:27:54.960 --> 00:27:58.480
of people just sit back on their 'Blessed Assurance'and

00:27:56.559 --> 00:28:01.279
say, 'Well, I'm going to

00:27:58.480 --> 00:28:03.120
just sow five dollars and

00:28:01.279 --> 00:28:04.720
we're going to have enough money to

00:28:03.120 --> 00:28:06.719
do whatever.'It starts out that way,

00:28:04.720 --> 00:28:11.080
but if you're faithful with little,

00:28:06.720 --> 00:28:11.080
he'll make you ruler over much.

00:28:11.120 --> 00:28:16.879
What's in your heavenly account?

00:28:15.039 --> 00:28:19.360
What are you doing to help your pastor

00:28:16.880 --> 00:28:21.360
out at your local church?

00:28:19.360 --> 00:28:23.279
'Well, I give him a dollar every time,'and

00:28:21.360 --> 00:28:26.559
you're worth hundreds of

00:28:23.279 --> 00:28:28.080
thousands. You

00:28:26.559 --> 00:28:30.480
can't even buy a stick of gum for a

00:28:28.080 --> 00:28:32.240
buck, but you think that pastor is going

00:28:30.480 --> 00:28:33.840
to be able to help and do things in his

00:28:32.240 --> 00:28:35.840
church to be able to get this gospel

00:28:33.840 --> 00:28:38.879
preached? You think, 'Well, I

00:28:41.279 --> 00:28:45.320
gave him five dollars, Brandon. I tipped him; he gave a good sermon today.'What

00:28:45.760 --> 00:28:49.200
are you

00:28:47.919 --> 00:28:50.720
going to do with five

00:28:49.200 --> 00:28:53.360
dollars?

00:28:50.720 --> 00:28:56.880
It's time to believe God for bigger.

00:28:53.360 --> 00:28:58.639
But then you look at what? Thirty, sixty, a hundredfold.

00:28:56.880 --> 00:29:03.200
What's in your heavenly

00:28:58.640 --> 00:29:04.480
account? Multiply a hundredfold of five dollars. Does

00:29:03.200 --> 00:29:06.880
that get you into millionaire

00:29:04.480 --> 00:29:11.960
status? No. Does that get you in the

00:29:06.880 --> 00:29:11.960
billionaire flow? No. It's a start,

00:29:12.000 --> 00:29:16.240
but you've got to check your thermostat

00:29:14.399 --> 00:29:17.840
and how much is in that account.

00:29:16.240 --> 00:29:20.080
That's where I multiply and I

00:29:17.840 --> 00:29:23.199
look and say, 'Okay, do I

00:29:20.080 --> 00:29:25.279
have by spiritual law the seed in the

00:29:23.200 --> 00:29:27.919
ground to believe for the building that

00:29:25.279 --> 00:29:29.600
the Lord has told me to do?

00:29:27.919 --> 00:29:31.520
Do I have it when he said, I want you to

00:29:29.600 --> 00:29:32.959
create new TV stations and do these

00:29:31.520 --> 00:29:34.720
things in the days ahead?'There are

00:29:32.960 --> 00:29:36.399
things that he's put a mandate on, like having

00:29:34.720 --> 00:29:38.000
a theater in Branson to do these

00:29:36.399 --> 00:29:39.918
things. But the Lord said,

00:29:38.000 --> 00:29:43.039
'Don't ever ask for

00:29:39.919 --> 00:29:45.520
anything; believe me for

00:29:43.039 --> 00:29:48.000
it.'The

00:29:45.520 --> 00:29:49.520
charismatic weirdness—like I said,

00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:51.120
the Lord said, 'I'm

00:29:49.520 --> 00:29:53.120
changing things. I'm going to do things

00:29:51.120 --> 00:29:54.639
differently

00:29:53.120 --> 00:29:56.080
with you

00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:58.960
and the way you're doing your ministry.

00:29:56.080 --> 00:30:02.080
I don't want it to be

00:29:58.960 --> 00:30:04.799
like this.'These people are

00:30:02.080 --> 00:30:07.760
losing their voice

00:30:04.799 --> 00:30:10.000
with the world.

00:30:07.760 --> 00:30:11.520
They're losing their—what was the word he

00:30:10.000 --> 00:30:12.080
used?

00:30:11.520 --> 00:30:13.679
relevance.

00:30:13.679 --> 00:30:19.200
Yeah, he said they're losing

00:30:15.919 --> 00:30:21.120
their relevance. They're not relevant.

00:30:19.200 --> 00:30:23.840
A lot of these people have lost their

00:30:21.120 --> 00:30:26.719
voice.

00:30:23.840 --> 00:30:30.720
And he said, 'Don't do what other men

00:30:26.720 --> 00:30:33.279
are doing. Do something different. Don't

00:30:30.720 --> 00:30:36.399
lose your voice because of the way you

00:30:33.279 --> 00:30:38.559
present my gospel.'They

00:30:36.399 --> 00:30:40.719
had their time and I told them to

00:30:38.559 --> 00:30:43.279
do that in their time, but

00:30:40.720 --> 00:30:47.320
behold, I'm doing something new.

00:30:43.279 --> 00:30:47.320
And so I just follow him.

00:30:47.360 --> 00:30:53.120
You can't go back to the way people did

00:30:50.559 --> 00:30:55.360
it before. God's doing something new in

00:30:53.120 --> 00:30:57.039
this generation.

00:30:55.360 --> 00:30:58.879
Well, you know, Oral Roberts did it this

00:30:57.039 --> 00:31:01.279
way, or somebody else.

00:31:01.279 --> 00:31:04.640
I try to always quote dead people

00:31:03.039 --> 00:31:06.960
because with the ones that are still

00:31:04.640 --> 00:31:09.279
alive,

00:31:06.960 --> 00:31:10.799
with

00:31:09.279 --> 00:31:13.039
the sin that's being uncovered

00:31:10.799 --> 00:31:16.639
in a lot of ministries, I try not to

00:31:13.039 --> 00:31:18.480
link up with anybody. I'm just

00:31:16.640 --> 00:31:19.840
going to stay in my lane

00:31:18.480 --> 00:31:21.600
because I know what he told me. There's

00:31:19.840 --> 00:31:23.678
a cleaning, and there's a lot of

00:31:21.600 --> 00:31:26.639
corruption in a lot of ministries. And

00:31:23.679 --> 00:31:28.399
the Lord said, 'I'm dealing with this.'It's

00:31:26.640 --> 00:31:31.120
embarrassing.

00:31:28.399 --> 00:31:33.520
You represent the King; you've got to get

00:31:31.120 --> 00:31:35.600
your stuff together. And the Lord said

00:31:33.520 --> 00:31:37.360
to me, 'Stay the course of what I told

00:31:35.600 --> 00:31:40.480
you to do.'And that's why I've never

00:31:37.360 --> 00:31:41.760
taken any invitations.

00:31:40.480 --> 00:31:44.399
How many people invite me to come

00:31:41.760 --> 00:31:46.000
